snippet.title: An Adventure and a Half - SM64 ROM Hack RELEASE & DOWNLOAD!
snippet.description:
A wacky little world with goofy mechanics, 1 and a half stars to collect!
Seriously, half stars ARE REAL though!
Check out @Arthurtilly , Inventor of the half star
*** DOWNLOAD: https://romhacking.com/hack/an-adventure-and-a-half ***

Like what I make? The best way to help out is if you want to spread the word and tell your friends about my mods!
I put MASSIVE amounts of work into my games. See previews of my other game, MIPS Forest ep. 1, here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRzRbTL5z06lnVhuY1FtfsS75R6c_46_M
Mystery of the Capsmith demo: https://youtu.be/XfAkOiU9s7w
My engine optimization: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRzRbTL5z06mot9aV6FU8ba9kkUPTQOax
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/dorrieal

SM64 ROM hack releases from me, both new and old: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLRzRbTL5z06lfgDRGWecznGPARS7t2RFi
I stream my game development live on Twitch: http://www.twitch.tv/dan_gptv

Subscribe to catch all releases and previews of every new adventure!
